[
  {
    "startTime": 13.44,
    "endTime": 15.44,
    "text": "it's story time"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.44,
    "endTime": 18.48,
    "text": "settle back and i'll begin"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.48,
    "endTime": 20.0,
    "text": "once upon a time"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.0,
    "endTime": 22.8,
    "text": "a mother duck sat patiently on her nest"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.8,
    "endTime": 25.84,
    "text": "of eggs waiting for them to hatch"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.84,
    "endTime": 27.84,
    "text": "and then one day she felt something move"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.84,
    "endTime": 29.119,
    "text": "beneath her"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.119,
    "endTime": 31.439,
    "text": "crack crack"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.439,
    "endTime": 33.28,
    "text": "filled with happiness she watched has"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.28,
    "endTime": 37.36,
    "text": "her eggs hatched one by one"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.52,
    "endTime": 39.04,
    "text": "i don't know about you but when i was"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.04,
    "endTime": 41.04,
    "text": "little story time was always one of my"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.04,
    "endTime": 43.04,
    "text": "favorite parts of the day"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.04,
    "endTime": 45.04,
    "text": "and i loved reading to my two sons when"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.04,
    "endTime": 47.28,
    "text": "they were small too"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.28,
    "endTime": 49.92,
    "text": "it's that special time when a parent and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.92,
    "endTime": 52.8,
    "text": "child can be totally absorbed together"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.8,
    "endTime": 54.64,
    "text": "in mystical kingdoms fantastical"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.64,
    "endTime": 56.8,
    "text": "beasties or scruffy little ducks that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.8,
    "endTime": 59.44,
    "text": "turn out to be swans"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.44,
    "endTime": 61.76,
    "text": "well that's how it is for some children"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.76,
    "endTime": 63.68,
    "text": "but for other children"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.68,
    "endTime": 65.76,
    "text": "there isn't a parent around to read to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.76,
    "endTime": 67.92,
    "text": "them"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.92,
    "endTime": 71.2,
    "text": "i'd like to tell you about sophie"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.2,
    "endTime": 73.52,
    "text": "sophie's five years old and lives with"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.52,
    "endTime": 75.92,
    "text": "her parents"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.92,
    "endTime": 78.24,
    "text": "one day there's a bang at the door"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.24,
    "endTime": 80.0,
    "text": "sophie hears lots of shouting her mum's"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.0,
    "endTime": 81.04,
    "text": "crying"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.04,
    "endTime": 83.2,
    "text": "she sees the police dragging her father"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.2,
    "endTime": 84.24,
    "text": "away"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.24,
    "endTime": 87.52,
    "text": "sophie's afraid she starts crying too"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.52,
    "endTime": 90.08,
    "text": "weeks go by sophie doesn't know what's"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.08,
    "endTime": 91.6,
    "text": "happened to her dad"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.6,
    "endTime": 93.92,
    "text": "when she asks her mum her mum gets upset"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.92,
    "endTime": 97.2,
    "text": "so she stops asking"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.28,
    "endTime": 99.2,
    "text": "sophie waits"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.2,
    "endTime": 101.759,
    "text": "she really misses her dad"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.759,
    "endTime": 103.439,
    "text": "every day she hurries home from school"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.439,
    "endTime": 105.92,
    "text": "in case he's come back"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.92,
    "endTime": 108.159,
    "text": "on many nights she cries herself to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.159,
    "endTime": 110.479,
    "text": "sleep"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.119,
    "endTime": 113.2,
    "text": "children at school start to tease her"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.2,
    "endTime": 115.2,
    "text": "they call her names"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.2,
    "endTime": 117.2,
    "text": "somebody's mum has heard that sophie's"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.2,
    "endTime": 120.0,
    "text": "dad is in prison"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.0,
    "endTime": 121.759,
    "text": "sophie pretends to be ill so she doesn't"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.759,
    "endTime": 123.6,
    "text": "have to go to school"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.6,
    "endTime": 125.68,
    "text": "and her teacher can't understand why"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.68,
    "endTime": 129.84,
    "text": "she's so far behind with her schoolwork"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.08,
    "endTime": 132.319,
    "text": "after what seems a long long time to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.319,
    "endTime": 133.76,
    "text": "sophie"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.76,
    "endTime": 136.879,
    "text": "a letter arrives it's from her dad the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.879,
    "endTime": 139.76,
    "text": "writing is very messy the letter makes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.76,
    "endTime": 141.04,
    "text": "her mum cry"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.04,
    "endTime": 143.84,
    "text": "but she reads a little out to sophie"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.84,
    "endTime": 145.68,
    "text": "he says that he's okay and that he's"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.68,
    "endTime": 147.599,
    "text": "missing them"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.599,
    "endTime": 149.92,
    "text": "it's a short letter"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.92,
    "endTime": 151.68,
    "text": "sophie says she'd like to go and see her"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.68,
    "endTime": 154.8,
    "text": "dad wherever he is but her mum says"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.8,
    "endTime": 156.959,
    "text": "it's too far away and they can't afford"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.959,
    "endTime": 158.64,
    "text": "the journey"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.64,
    "endTime": 160.959,
    "text": "then one day the phone rings"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.959,
    "endTime": 162.16,
    "text": "sophie"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.16,
    "endTime": 164.8,
    "text": "come and speak to daddy"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.8,
    "endTime": 166.72,
    "text": "that sounds different"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.72,
    "endTime": 168.48,
    "text": "far away"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.48,
    "endTime": 170.319,
    "text": "he says he can't talk for very long and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.319,
    "endTime": 173.36,
    "text": "anyway it's very noisy wherever he is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.36,
    "endTime": 174.879,
    "text": "and sophie"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.879,
    "endTime": 178.239,
    "text": "doesn't know what to say to him"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.48,
    "endTime": 180.239,
    "text": "well as stories go that's not a very"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.239,
    "endTime": 183.2,
    "text": "nice one in the united kingdom"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.2,
    "endTime": 186.08,
    "text": "hundred thousand children"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.08,
    "endTime": 188.959,
    "text": "experience the shame and isolation of a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.959,
    "endTime": 191.12,
    "text": "parent in prison"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.12,
    "endTime": 193.76,
    "text": "two hundred thousand that's more than"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.76,
    "endTime": 195.68,
    "text": "the number of children each year who are"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.68,
    "endTime": 198.319,
    "text": "affected by their parents divorcing and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.319,
    "endTime": 200.0,
    "text": "it can affect the children of prisoners"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.0,
    "endTime": 201.599,
    "text": "very deeply"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.599,
    "endTime": 203.12,
    "text": "there can be problems at school and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.12,
    "endTime": 205.28,
    "text": "they're three times more likely to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.28,
    "endTime": 208.8,
    "text": "suffer from mental health issues"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.8,
    "endTime": 211.68,
    "text": "in so many ways children are the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.68,
    "endTime": 214.4,
    "text": "unintended victims of their parents"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.4,
    "endTime": 215.68,
    "text": "crimes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.68,
    "endTime": 217.28,
    "text": "in so many ways"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.28,
    "endTime": 219.76,
    "text": "children are the overlooked victims of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.76,
    "endTime": 222.959,
    "text": "their parents crimes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.84,
    "endTime": 226.08,
    "text": "until last november i was a serving"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.08,
    "endTime": 228.799,
    "text": "prisoner imprisoned for fraud"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228.799,
    "endTime": 232.319,
    "text": "i was dishonest and i paid the penalty"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.319,
    "endTime": 233.92,
    "text": "before that i'd been a practicing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.92,
    "endTime": 236.08,
    "text": "solicitor for 30 years"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236.08,
    "endTime": 238.799,
    "text": "i'd had a happy and stable upbringing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 238.799,
    "endTime": 241.12,
    "text": "a good education a happy marriage which"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.12,
    "endTime": 244.239,
    "text": "i'm pleased to say continues i have two"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 244.239,
    "endTime": 246.239,
    "text": "adult sons"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246.239,
    "endTime": 247.92,
    "text": "when they were growing up i did my best"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.92,
    "endTime": 249.92,
    "text": "to be around for them"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.92,
    "endTime": 252.239,
    "text": "as much as i could and i took a careful"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 252.239,
    "endTime": 254.72,
    "text": "interest in what they did i read to my"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.72,
    "endTime": 256.639,
    "text": "boys every night"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.639,
    "endTime": 260.32,
    "text": "and ironically our favorite story was"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 260.32,
    "endTime": 263.04,
    "text": "burglar bill"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.04,
    "endTime": 267.28,
    "text": "but when i got to prison it soon became"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267.28,
    "endTime": 269.759,
    "text": "apparent that my background was very"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.759,
    "endTime": 271.12,
    "text": "different to that of most other"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.12,
    "endTime": 272.479,
    "text": "prisoners"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.479,
    "endTime": 274.16,
    "text": "few of the men that i met had had a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.16,
    "endTime": 277.52,
    "text": "decent education indeed many associated"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 277.52,
    "endTime": 280.479,
    "text": "education with humiliation and failure i"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 280.479,
    "endTime": 283.04,
    "text": "can tell you firsthand that prison is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.04,
    "endTime": 285.52,
    "text": "dehumanizing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 285.52,
    "endTime": 287.6,
    "text": "prisoners hard enough they shut down"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 287.6,
    "endTime": 289.759,
    "text": "they close in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 289.759,
    "endTime": 292.0,
    "text": "just to survive"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 292.0,
    "endTime": 296.479,
    "text": "and this can be devastating for families"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 296.479,
    "endTime": 299.12,
    "text": "in fact maintaining contact with your"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 299.12,
    "endTime": 301.759,
    "text": "family from prison can be very difficult"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 301.759,
    "endTime": 303.44,
    "text": "indeed"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 303.44,
    "endTime": 305.04,
    "text": "and if a child does get to see their"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 305.04,
    "endTime": 306.639,
    "text": "parents in prison"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 306.639,
    "endTime": 308.16,
    "text": "they have to go through the same pat"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 308.16,
    "endTime": 310.24,
    "text": "down searches as the adults they walk"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 310.24,
    "endTime": 312.8,
    "text": "through the same detector frames they're"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 312.8,
    "endTime": 315.12,
    "text": "sniffed by the same sniffer dogs but all"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 315.12,
    "endTime": 316.56,
    "text": "because some children have been the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 316.56,
    "endTime": 319.52,
    "text": "unwitting carriers of drugs and mobile"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 319.52,
    "endTime": 321.36,
    "text": "phones"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 321.36,
    "endTime": 322.8,
    "text": "and when they get through to see their"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 322.8,
    "endTime": 324.96,
    "text": "parent they may be tired from a long"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 324.96,
    "endTime": 326.479,
    "text": "journey"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 326.479,
    "endTime": 329.68,
    "text": "shy tongue-tied even upset"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 329.68,
    "endTime": 331.6,
    "text": "and it isn't easy for the parents who"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 331.6,
    "endTime": 334.08,
    "text": "may not be getting along"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 334.08,
    "endTime": 336.88,
    "text": "for many reasons not just these"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 336.88,
    "endTime": 339.36,
    "text": "over half of prisoners lose contact with"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 339.36,
    "endTime": 341.84,
    "text": "their children and families"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 341.84,
    "endTime": 343.84,
    "text": "how can we help prisoners to stay in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 343.84,
    "endTime": 346.4,
    "text": "contact with their families"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 346.4,
    "endTime": 348.0,
    "text": "when i was a prisoner at channing's wood"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 348.0,
    "endTime": 350.16,
    "text": "prison i began working for a charity"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 350.16,
    "endTime": 352.8,
    "text": "called storybook dance"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 352.8,
    "endTime": 355.759,
    "text": "storybook dance began in 2003 when"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 355.759,
    "endTime": 358.479,
    "text": "sharon berry a civilian worker in a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 358.479,
    "endTime": 361.12,
    "text": "prison realized just how much many"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 361.12,
    "endTime": 362.96,
    "text": "prisoners wanted to stay in contact with"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 362.96,
    "endTime": 364.56,
    "text": "their children"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 364.56,
    "endTime": 366.96,
    "text": "and so armed with a few story books"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 366.96,
    "endTime": 368.72,
    "text": "she began to help prisoners to read and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 368.72,
    "endTime": 371.12,
    "text": "record stories to send home to their"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 371.12,
    "endTime": 372.319,
    "text": "children"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 372.319,
    "endTime": 375.28,
    "text": "it wasn't a new idea few ideas like this"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 375.28,
    "endTime": 376.479,
    "text": "are new"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 376.479,
    "endTime": 378.8,
    "text": "they're great ideas"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 378.8,
    "endTime": 382.319,
    "text": "but it was an instant success"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 382.319,
    "endTime": 385.28,
    "text": "you may wonder how does the recording"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 385.28,
    "endTime": 387.68,
    "text": "of the stories work in prison"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 387.68,
    "endTime": 389.84,
    "text": "is it difficult for prisoners"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 389.84,
    "endTime": 392.88,
    "text": "can it be challenging"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 393.199,
    "endTime": 395.36,
    "text": "well the process of choosing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 395.36,
    "endTime": 397.919,
    "text": "reading and recording the story"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 397.919,
    "endTime": 401.68,
    "text": "can be very challenging for prisoners"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 402.0,
    "endTime": 404.0,
    "text": "prison is tough"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 404.0,
    "endTime": 406.08,
    "text": "and prisoners can't afford to show any"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 406.08,
    "endTime": 410.08,
    "text": "signs of weakness or vulnerability"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 410.08,
    "endTime": 413.199,
    "text": "but this this recording process"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 413.199,
    "endTime": 414.56,
    "text": "this can be"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 414.56,
    "endTime": 417.199,
    "text": "uncomfortable upsetting sometimes all"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 417.199,
    "endTime": 420.639,
    "text": "just a bit too much"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 421.759,
    "endTime": 424.639,
    "text": "and prisoners often cry"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 424.639,
    "endTime": 427.44,
    "text": "they cry because they regret missing out"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 427.44,
    "endTime": 429.52,
    "text": "on their children's lives"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 429.52,
    "endTime": 431.599,
    "text": "they cry because they're ashamed that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 431.599,
    "endTime": 433.68,
    "text": "they've let their families down"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 433.68,
    "endTime": 435.919,
    "text": "they cry because they don't know how to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 435.919,
    "endTime": 440.08,
    "text": "go about reading to their children"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 440.16,
    "endTime": 442.4,
    "text": "but because when they come to us"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 442.4,
    "endTime": 445.759,
    "text": "we offer a private space one-to-one"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 445.759,
    "endTime": 448.8,
    "text": "prisoners don't need to be tough anymore"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 448.8,
    "endTime": 450.72,
    "text": "and they can use their vulnerability as"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 450.72,
    "endTime": 451.84,
    "text": "a strength"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 451.84,
    "endTime": 455.84,
    "text": "when contacting with their children"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 455.84,
    "endTime": 457.52,
    "text": "i remember one prisoner who came to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 457.52,
    "endTime": 458.96,
    "text": "record"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 458.96,
    "endTime": 461.44,
    "text": "he was a big hard man with a reputation"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 461.44,
    "endTime": 463.199,
    "text": "for being tough"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 463.199,
    "endTime": 465.68,
    "text": "he came along as implacable as ever but"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 465.68,
    "endTime": 467.12,
    "text": "when the door of the recording room"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 467.12,
    "endTime": 469.759,
    "text": "closed behind him that facade began to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 469.759,
    "endTime": 470.8,
    "text": "crumble"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 470.8,
    "endTime": 472.72,
    "text": "from his pocket he took a screwed-up"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 472.72,
    "endTime": 475.199,
    "text": "piece of paper and quietly began to read"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 475.199,
    "endTime": 477.12,
    "text": "the words which he'd written"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 477.12,
    "endTime": 480.4,
    "text": "as a message for his two little ones"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 480.4,
    "endTime": 483.12,
    "text": "his hands were shaking"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 483.12,
    "endTime": 486.4,
    "text": "and then in a surprisingly quiet voice"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 486.4,
    "endTime": 490.56,
    "text": "he began to sing their favorite lullaby"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 490.56,
    "endTime": 492.479,
    "text": "you see there wasn't much that he could"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 492.479,
    "endTime": 494.72,
    "text": "do from behind bars to show his children"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 494.72,
    "endTime": 496.72,
    "text": "that he missed and loved them"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 496.72,
    "endTime": 500.0,
    "text": "but he could do this"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 500.639,
    "endTime": 502.639,
    "text": "once the recording is made"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 502.639,
    "endTime": 504.879,
    "text": "it's sent to the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 504.879,
    "endTime": 507.28,
    "text": "storybook dance production unit at"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 507.28,
    "endTime": 509.759,
    "text": "channingswood prison"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 509.759,
    "endTime": 511.12,
    "text": "in devon"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 511.12,
    "endTime": 513.2,
    "text": "and that's where i worked"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 513.2,
    "endTime": 515.68,
    "text": "i was trained along with other prisoners"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 515.68,
    "endTime": 518.399,
    "text": "to edit and produce recordings sent in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 518.399,
    "endTime": 522.479,
    "text": "from prisons all over the united kingdom"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 522.719,
    "endTime": 526.72,
    "text": "using audio and video software"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 526.72,
    "endTime": 528.16,
    "text": "the recordings"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 528.16,
    "endTime": 530.72,
    "text": "have the mistakes taken out"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 530.72,
    "endTime": 531.6,
    "text": "and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 531.6,
    "endTime": 535.36,
    "text": "sound effects and music added in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 535.36,
    "endTime": 536.16,
    "text": "and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 536.16,
    "endTime": 538.959,
    "text": "the experience and skill which the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 538.959,
    "endTime": 541.2,
    "text": "prison editors gain"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 541.2,
    "endTime": 545.36,
    "text": "helps them in their future employment"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 546.16,
    "endTime": 548.959,
    "text": "once the recording is finalized it's"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 548.959,
    "endTime": 552.24,
    "text": "transferred to a cd or a dvd"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 552.24,
    "endTime": 554.32,
    "text": "and sent out to the families so that the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 554.32,
    "endTime": 556.88,
    "text": "children can watch them whenever they"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 556.88,
    "endTime": 559.76,
    "text": "feel the need"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 560.0,
    "endTime": 562.56,
    "text": "and they listen to these recordings and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 562.56,
    "endTime": 563.68,
    "text": "watch them"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 563.68,
    "endTime": 566.16,
    "text": "a lot"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 566.48,
    "endTime": 568.399,
    "text": "at bedtime"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 568.399,
    "endTime": 569.839,
    "text": "in the car"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 569.839,
    "endTime": 572.24,
    "text": "some even take them to school to show"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 572.24,
    "endTime": 574.399,
    "text": "their friends"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 574.399,
    "endTime": 577.6,
    "text": "these recordings they show the children"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 577.6,
    "endTime": 579.839,
    "text": "that they're loved and missed"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 579.839,
    "endTime": 581.6,
    "text": "and they show the prisoner"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 581.6,
    "endTime": 583.839,
    "text": "that they can do something for their"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 583.839,
    "endTime": 587.12,
    "text": "child as a parent"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 587.12,
    "endTime": 589.12,
    "text": "how do you remember sophie"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 589.12,
    "endTime": 592.0,
    "text": "well one day just before christmas"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 592.0,
    "endTime": 593.68,
    "text": "a parcel arrived"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 593.68,
    "endTime": 595.92,
    "text": "and this is what was in it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 595.92,
    "endTime": 599.08,
    "text": "let's listen to a little of it together"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 599.08,
    "endTime": 602.229,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 606.48,
    "endTime": 608.959,
    "text": "higher and higher they flew"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 608.959,
    "endTime": 612.8,
    "text": "across land across oceans they spared"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 612.8,
    "endTime": 614.64,
    "text": "through the magical northern lights they"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 614.64,
    "endTime": 615.76,
    "text": "passed"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 615.76,
    "endTime": 619.32,
    "text": "i'd love to see"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 621.99,
    "endTime": 626.878,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 627.6,
    "endTime": 629.279,
    "text": "they visited all the children in the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 629.279,
    "endTime": 631.519,
    "text": "world and left presents for each and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 631.519,
    "endTime": 633.44,
    "text": "every one"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 633.44,
    "endTime": 635.76,
    "text": "in the blink of an eye they were back in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 635.76,
    "endTime": 639.48,
    "text": "front of the bottom field"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 642.64,
    "endTime": 651.099,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 657.92,
    "endTime": 659.36,
    "text": "sophie and her mum listened to that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 659.36,
    "endTime": 661.6,
    "text": "three times and they haven't laughed so"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 661.6,
    "endTime": 663.2,
    "text": "much in a long time"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 663.2,
    "endTime": 664.88,
    "text": "they can see that he's all right they"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 664.88,
    "endTime": 666.399,
    "text": "can see that he loves them and the next"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 666.399,
    "endTime": 667.76,
    "text": "time he rings"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 667.76,
    "endTime": 669.92,
    "text": "sophie's got plenty to talk about what"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 669.92,
    "endTime": 671.76,
    "text": "does charlie the champion"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 671.76,
    "endTime": 675.2,
    "text": "will daddy do another story very soon"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 675.2,
    "endTime": 678.88,
    "text": "since it began in 2003 storybook dance"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 678.88,
    "endTime": 682.16,
    "text": "has grown and grown"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 682.16,
    "endTime": 684.64,
    "text": "it now operates as storybook dance and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 684.64,
    "endTime": 686.959,
    "text": "storybook mums in more than a hundred"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 686.959,
    "endTime": 689.44,
    "text": "prisons in the united kingdom"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 689.44,
    "endTime": 691.68,
    "text": "98"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 691.68,
    "endTime": 693.68,
    "text": "of the prisoners who take part say that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 693.68,
    "endTime": 695.44,
    "text": "it's improved their relationship with"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 695.44,
    "endTime": 697.44,
    "text": "their child"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 697.44,
    "endTime": 698.76,
    "text": "and since"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 698.76,
    "endTime": 704.64,
    "text": "2003 over 60 000 dvds and cds have been"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 704.64,
    "endTime": 708.48,
    "text": "sent out to the children of prisoners"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 710.32,
    "endTime": 712.64,
    "text": "for sophie's family and for thousands of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 712.64,
    "endTime": 714.88,
    "text": "families like them storybook dance has"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 714.88,
    "endTime": 717.76,
    "text": "been a lifeline"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 717.76,
    "endTime": 719.6,
    "text": "some prisoners say that it's the first"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 719.6,
    "endTime": 721.04,
    "text": "time that they've begun to build a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 721.04,
    "endTime": 723.68,
    "text": "relationship with their child"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 723.68,
    "endTime": 725.44,
    "text": "and some poor readers have been so"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 725.44,
    "endTime": 727.2,
    "text": "inspired by what they've been able to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 727.2,
    "endTime": 729.2,
    "text": "achieve that they've gone to education"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 729.2,
    "endTime": 730.959,
    "text": "classes to improve their own reading"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 730.959,
    "endTime": 733.44,
    "text": "skills"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 733.92,
    "endTime": 735.36,
    "text": "let's go back"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 735.36,
    "endTime": 737.04,
    "text": "to the story of the ugly duckling but"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 737.04,
    "endTime": 739.2,
    "text": "this time i'd like to play you a"
  },
