    "startTime": 792.8,
    "endTime": 795.76,
    "text": "a recording an excerpt of the recording"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 795.76,
    "endTime": 798.24,
    "text": "with the mentor's voice taken out"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 798.24,
    "endTime": 801.92,
    "text": "and sound effects and music added in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 801.92,
    "endTime": 804.079,
    "text": "he had nowhere to ride"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 804.079,
    "endTime": 807.36,
    "text": "then one day he got away he ran until he"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 807.36,
    "endTime": 809.68,
    "text": "come to the great marsh where the wild"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 809.68,
    "endTime": 812.399,
    "text": "dogs lived and he laid in rushes for two"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 812.399,
    "endTime": 815.399,
    "text": "weeks"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 815.519,
    "endTime": 818.16,
    "text": "some wild dogs and geese come to look at"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 818.16,
    "endTime": 820.88,
    "text": "him you're very ugly they said and they"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 820.88,
    "endTime": 824.36,
    "text": "laughed at him"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 828.32,
    "endTime": 830.639,
    "text": "the ugly duckling ran away"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 830.639,
    "endTime": 832.5,
    "text": "from the great marsh"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 832.5,
    "endTime": 836.0,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 836.0,
    "endTime": 840.72,
    "text": "and this is how he finished the story"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 841.279,
    "endTime": 844.16,
    "text": "he wasn't an ugly duckling at all during"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 844.16,
    "endTime": 846.959,
    "text": "the winter he had grown into a beautiful"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 846.959,
    "endTime": 848.72,
    "text": "white swan"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 848.72,
    "endTime": 851.04,
    "text": "the other swans has looked at him and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 851.04,
    "endTime": 853.44,
    "text": "thought how beautiful he was"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 853.44,
    "endTime": 858.88,
    "text": "come with us they said and he did"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 861.47,
    "endTime": 864.32,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 864.32,
    "endTime": 866.959,
    "text": "well tiara i hope you have enjoyed this"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 866.959,
    "endTime": 867.92,
    "text": "story"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 867.92,
    "endTime": 870.48,
    "text": "as much as i enjoyed reading this story"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 870.48,
    "endTime": 871.839,
    "text": "to you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 871.839,
    "endTime": 874.32,
    "text": "i cannot wait to be with you again and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 874.32,
    "endTime": 876.639,
    "text": "hold you in my arms"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 876.639,
    "endTime": 879.199,
    "text": "all my love your daddy owen"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 879.199,
    "endTime": 880.72,
    "text": "lots of love i miss you with all my"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 880.72,
    "endTime": 884.3,
    "text": "heart goodbye for now my life bye-bye"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 884.3,
    "endTime": 890.289,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 894.16,
    "endTime": 895.6,
    "text": "when he listened to that recording in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 895.6,
    "endTime": 897.279,
    "text": "his cell before it was sent out to his"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 897.279,
    "endTime": 898.72,
    "text": "daughter"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 898.72,
    "endTime": 900.0,
    "text": "he cried"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 900.0,
    "endTime": 901.68,
    "text": "and that's a pretty common reaction from"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 901.68,
    "endTime": 904.0,
    "text": "prisoners as they realize for the first"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 904.0,
    "endTime": 905.68,
    "text": "time they've been able to do something"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 905.68,
    "endTime": 907.839,
    "text": "for their child which they never thought"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 907.839,
    "endTime": 909.68,
    "text": "they could"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 909.68,
    "endTime": 911.36,
    "text": "they've connected in the most"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 911.36,
    "endTime": 914.16,
    "text": "fundamental way through the medium of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 914.16,
    "endTime": 916.24,
    "text": "storytelling"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 916.24,
    "endTime": 918.48,
    "text": "and as for sophie"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 918.48,
    "endTime": 921.89,
    "text": "she wants the gruffalo next time"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 921.89,
    "endTime": 925.86,
    "text": "[Applause]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 928.56,
    "endTime": 930.639,
    "text": "you"
  }
